{"tid":833743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 39 吋 胸 肌 想 露 股","createTime":"2018-09-23T17:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T00:03:30.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"818462e0c8a0fd677d1ce9e9c81a8076bc84e0eb","tid":833743,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤到電台出席職安健活動，最近大隻不少的他被問到胸肌幾大，他說：「目測39吋。（冇度過？）自己揸過，C Cup！不過唔知係唔係，你使唔使測試吓？」提到正在拍攝劇集《殺手》，他指監製陳維冠拍《誇世代》時已想他露肉：「今次佢話有機會畀我露上身，我隨時露得，有信心嘅，都唔錯，由細到大都比較翹。（喺公眾浴室要小心？）所以要注意職業安全，任何地方都注意安全，跣親就唔好。」<br />\n<br />\n提到可試過被𥄫？他表示沒有：「大家都好規矩，我望人啫。（想練到胸肌幾大？）唔使太大嘅，諗緊新劇使唔使加啲情節露肉，我有一場畀人捉咗，睇吓會唔會衣衫襤褸，借啲意鎅穿自己件衫，機會係自己爭取㗎嘛。（想做脫星？）唔係，露少少、性感少少啫。（怕唔怕畀人話你改劇本？）唔會，監製接受能力好強。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908160943768-0908_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180908211046\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908160943768-0908_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180908211046&h=381320fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f08196b45d360720bd62f0628a51d3e27a172061","tid":833743,"uid":188396,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"佢幾時收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d073db255647497e31456f8658c448bffe67338","tid":833743,"uid":166726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"究竟點解佢真係可以咁撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ea283e9294e95004fcd74910943b71964b820e","tid":833743,"uid":157000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"個膊咁A既<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d99089ffaf5968d001229101ccbbbef00bb0723","tid":833743,"uid":119330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57ea283e9294e95004fcd74910943b71964b820